layout.house_prompt: A Jurassic Park themed kids bedroom. The room features a bed with Jurassic Park dinosaur bedding, a Jurassic Park themed rug on the floor, and a Jurassic Park poster on the wall. Two dinosaur stuffed animals sit on the bed, and a dinosaur themed desk lamp rests on the nightstand.

bedroom.text_description: A Jurassic Park themed kids bedroom. The room features a bed with Jurassic Park dinosaur bedding, a Jurassic Park themed rug on the floor, and a Jurassic Park poster on the wall. Two dinosaur stuffed animals sit on the bed, and a dinosaur themed desk lamp rests on the nightstand.
